thing better?

03:31.590 --> 03:33.454
No, the lighter one
is best.

03:33.489 --> 03:35.422
When would you ever want
the lighter one of anything?

03:35.456 --> 03:38.632
A summer coat? A soufflé?
A case of chicken pox?

03:38.666 --> 03:40.979
